media: v4l2-tpg-core: Add support for 32-bit packed YUV formats (v2)

Add support for the following formats to tpg:
 V4L2_PIX_FMT_AYUV32
 V4L2_PIX_FMT_XYUV32
 V4L2_PIX_FMT_VUYA32
 V4L2_PIX_FMT_VUYX32

Changes from v1:
Remove the duplicate case value

